<br>
The below test is done using Basic Comparisons...The numbers are Averages taken from some board magelos/Myself.<br>
<br>
Both the enchanter and the magician have 3100 mana.<br>
Both the enchanter and the Magician Have C3 Active on them.<br>
Spec/Mod rods were not counted in the comparison as chanters can also specilize in evoc and use mod rods. <br>
<br>
I gave the mages c3 because simply the 5 minute encounter below is a raid comparison and both the mage and the enc should be buffed. I did not however give them Both PoTG because it would have simply inflated the numbers. Both have a standing mana regen of 15 mana per tick.<br>
<br>
This test is done only using standing mana regen...I am doing another one now using med times however due to work I dont have the time to finish it out (it will be much longer). I have a feeling however in the med time ones it will be almost even but the mage might have an edge.<br>
<br>
The below fight is using a 5 minute fight....Many luclin fights run 30 minutes while mana kunark fights run 1 minute...So I chose an &quot;in between&quot; number...Here is the blow by blow.<br>
<br>
Both can cast 11 times before going oom. The mage will take aprox 99 seconds to cast his mana bar while the chanter will take  154 seconds.....OR 17 ticks for the mage/ 26 ticks for the enchanter. During this time the mage will have regened 255 mana the enc will have regened 390.<br>
<br>
1:39 seconds into the fight mage deals 11,000 Dmg 255 mana<br>
2:32 seconds into the fight enc deals 12100 dmg 390 mana<br>
+3 ticks later (18 seconds)<br>
1:57 seconds into the fight Mage 12,000 damage 25 Mana<br>
2:50 seconds into the fight 13,200 damage 160 Mana<br>
+7 ticks later (42 seconds.)<br>
2:39 seconds into the fight mage 12000 damage 130 mana.<br>
3:32 seconds into the fight enc 13200 dmg 265 mana.<br>
+2 ticks later (12 seconds)<br>
2:51 seconds into the fight mage 12000 damage 160 mana<br>
3:44 seconds into the fight enc 14300 damage 20 mana<br>
+9 ticks later (54 seconds)<br>
3:45 seconds into the fight. Mage 13000 Damage 20 mana<br>
4:39 seconds into the fight enc 14300 Damage 155 Mana<br>
<br>
Ech tick + I went through I calculated in cast time+recast time and gave them mana regen for both...I also used the cast time+recast time to write in the next tick shown. After the last point shown neither class will regen enough mana for another nuke. The finale results are.<br>
<br>
Mage DPS Using the pure magic nuke. 43.3 DPS. 13000 dmg.<br>
Enc DPS Using the pure magic nuke. 47.7 DPS 14300 dmg.<br>
<br>
Pretty close...I think when I finally get to do the med times the numbers will be diffrent.<br>
